Jupter Notebook Shortcuts

shift-enter | execute current cell
command + enter | run selected cells
alt + enter | run current cell and insert below


esc on cell = command mode
enter in command mode = edit mode

command mode
h | help
H | show all shorcuts
shift + up | extend selcted cells above
shift + below | extend selected cells below
c | copy
v | paste
x | cut
z | undo
a | creates a cell above
b | creates a cell below
shift + m | merge cells together
cntrl, shift, - | seperate cells
m | markdown mode
y | code mode
r | raw mode
d + d | delete selected cells
shift + space | scroll notebook up
ctrl + home | go to cell start
ctrl + end | go to end cell


select cells 
f | find and replace

